1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-400 shrink-0"></span>Established TypeScript-first development standards with Biome and Husky, reducing production bugs by 40%</li><li class="flex gap-3 text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-sm"><span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-400 shrink-0"></span>Integrated AI-assisted development workflows (Claude in VS Code), accelerating feature delivery by 30%</li><li class="flex gap-3 text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-sm"><span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-400 shrink-0"></span>Implemented Figma-to-React workflow using MCP, streamlining UI development and design handoff</li><li class="flex gap-3 text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-sm"><span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-400 shrink-0"></span>Mentored 5 junior developers in React Native best practices and modern JavaScript patterns</li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="relative md:pl-12" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px)"><div class="absolute left-0 top-6 hidden md:flex items-center justify-center w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-page)] border-2 border-indigo-500/50 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-briefcase w-4 h-4 text-indigo-400" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 20V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="6" rx="2"></rect></svg></div><div class="rounded-2xl border transition-all cursor-pointer bg-[var(--bg-card)] border-[var(--border-soft)] hover:border-indigo-500/20"><div class="p-5"><div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4"><div class="flex-1"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap mb-1"><h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-semibold text-lg">Hybrid Mobile App Developer</h3></div><p class="text-indigo-400 font-medium">BlueCrimson</p><div class="flex items-center gap-4